  <num>16-4416</num>
  <heading>Representation by lawyer.</heading>
  <text>A party to an arbitration proceeding may be represented by a lawyer.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 17-111" type="History">Feb. 27, 2008, D.C. Law 17-111, § 2(b), 55 DCR 1847</annotation>
    <annotation type="Editor's Notes">Uniform Law: This section is based upon § 16 of the Uniform Arbitration Act (2000).</annotation>
